name: Don't Enter
description:
Don't Enter is a short horror game that was made for the Spooktober Jam.

Warning: WebGL build might be broken, if you find any bugs in it try switching to the standalone version.

Controls:

AD to move
E to interact (you can skip text by holding down E)
